          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "content": "<p>Sustainability starts with the design of our Voxblock players, books, and packaging.<br\/><br\/>Our players have a minimalist design, using the fewest possible component parts, meaning they are <strong>easily repairable <\/strong>and ensuring a long life.<\/p><p>Our audiobooks are made from <strong>eco-friendly materials<\/strong>, crafted from 97% recycled paper and card held together with biodegradable glue. <\/p><p>We use 100% <strong>recyclable and plastic free packaging<\/strong>.<\/p>"
          }
